WEBVTT

00:03:29.706 --> 00:03:31.500
like your eyes, your nose, your ears,

00:03:31.524 --> 00:03:33.003
fingers or toes?

00:03:33.027 --> 00:03:34.997
What about your teeth?

00:03:35.021 --> 00:03:37.450
What are the odds of you
keeping your dental health

00:03:37.474 --> 00:03:38.503
for a hundred years?

00:03:38.527 --> 00:03:39.995
A thousand years?

00:03:40.019 --> 00:03:42.346
One million years?

00:03:42.370 --> 00:03:45.525
You might end up looking like
a horribly scuffed-up Mr. Potato Head

00:03:45.549 --> 00:03:47.851
with missing pieces and dentures.

00:03:47.875 --> 00:03:51.152
So, are you sure you want to live forever?

00:03:52.041 --> 00:03:56.652
Now, which superpower physics lesson
will you explore next?

00:03:56.676 --> 00:04:01.059
Shifting body size and content,